<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Bid Received - IpTruck</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #27ae60;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .bid-details {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .price-highlight {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            color: #155724;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .truck-info {
            background-color: #e8f4f8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .driver-info {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .urgent-tag {
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>📩 New Bid Received!</h1>
        <p>A carrier has submitted a bid for your booking</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="urgent-tag">
            🚨 ACTION REQUIRED
        </div>
        
        <h2>Bid Details</h2>
        
        <div class="bid-details">
            <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
            <p><strong>Bid ID:</strong> <%= bidId %></p>
            <p><strong>Carrier Company:</strong> <%= carrierCompany %></p>
            <p><strong>Contact Person:</strong> <%= contactPerson %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="price-highlight">
            💰 Bid Amount: ₦<%= bidAmount %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="truck-info">
            <h3>🚛 Truck Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Make & Model:</strong> <%= truckMakeModel %></p>
            <p><strong>Year:</strong> <%= truckYear %></p>
            <p><strong>License Plate:</strong> <%= truckLicensePlate %></p>
            <p><strong>Max Payload:</strong> <%= maxPayload %> kg</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="driver-info">
            <h3>👨‍💼 Driver Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= driverName %></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= driverPhone %></p>
            <p><strong>Experience:</strong> <%= driverExperience %> years</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bid-details">
            <h3>📅 Proposed Timeline</h3>
            <p><strong>Pickup Date:</strong> <%= proposedPickupTime %></p>
            <p><strong>Delivery Date:</strong> <%= estimatedDeliveryTime %></p>
        </div>
        
        <% if (message) { %>
        <div class="bid-details">
            <h3>💬 Message from Carrier</h3>
            <p><em>"<%= message %>"</em></p>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <center>
            <a href="<%= bidUrl %>" class="button">Review Bid Details</a>
        </center>
        
        <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>📋 Review the bid details carefully</li>
            <li>📞 Contact the carrier if you have questions</li>
            <li>✅ Accept the bid if you're satisfied</li>
            <li>❌ Decline if it doesn't meet your requirements</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>💡 Tips for choosing the best bid:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Compare prices and delivery times</li>
            <li>Check the carrier's rating and reviews</li>
            <li>Verify truck specifications match your needs</li>
            <li>Consider the driver's experience</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Need Help?</strong></p>
        <p>If you need assistance reviewing bids or have questions about the booking process, contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a></p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The IpTruck Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2024 IpTruck. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You received this email because a new bid was submitted for your booking.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
